FBIS4-45098 "jpnea034___94047" JPRS-NEA-94-034 JPRS Near East & South Asia 8 May 1994 SOUTH ASIA IRAN Over 600 Kg Opium Seized in Fars Province Over 600 Kg Opium Seized in Fars Province 94LA0178H Tehran JAHAN-E ESLAM in Persian 8 May 94 p 3 94LA0178H Tehran JAHAN-E ESLAM Persian CSO [Text] Police antinarcotics officials seized 605 kg of opium in Shiraz, Darab, Lamard, and Nayriz in Fars Province. The Fars Police Precinct public relations official said on Saturday: This opium was seized during the last few days from passing vehicles, and the distribution agents were identified. According to him, several of the primary defendants involved in distributing the opium were arrested and turned over to judicial officials.
